AI Mastery Program

A structured 3-phase journey from understanding Generative AI fundamentals to building production-ready autonomous agents.

Phase 1: Foundation

Understanding Generative AI

Mastered the vocabulary and core concepts distinguishing Generative AI from traditional ML. Completed Google Cloud's Introduction to Generative AI.

Prompt Engineering Mastery

Learned programmatic LLM interaction through DeepLearning.AI's ChatGPT Prompt Engineering for Developers.

Phase 2: Builder

LangChain for LLM Applications

Built end-to-end LLM applications mastering chains, memory, and retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) patterns.

Production LLM Systems

Focused on evaluation, safety guardrails, and building reliable systems with the ChatGPT API through DeepLearning.AI.

Phase 3: Agent

Agentic RAG with LlamaIndex

Created autonomous agents capable of multi-step reasoning, tool use, and complex decision-making workflows.

Multi-Agent Systems

Building systems where multiple agents collaborate to solve complex problems beyond single-agent capabilities.
